name: VSAccountAccessStatus
desc: Constants that represent your app’s access status to the user’s subscription information.

items.name: case denied
items.desc: The user denied the app access to subscription information.

items.name: case granted
items.desc: The user allowed the app to access subscription information.

items.name: case notDetermined
items.desc: The user hasn’t chosen whether to allow the app to access subscription information.

items.name: case restricted
items.desc: The app isn’t allowed to access subscription information.
